- Cases are registered in static arrays at compile time
- Negative (rejection/fail) tests use `buc_die` exit codes (non-zero) to signal failure
- Run via `tt/rbw-tf.FixtureRun.sh <fixture-name>` tabtarget which invokes the compiled `rbtd` binary
- Fixture must be registered in `RBTDRC_FIXTURES` global and added to applicable suites in `RBTDRC_SUITES`
